title: Clinton, aides stressed protecting State Dept info in email
text: Clinton, aides stressed protecting State Dept info in email Tuesday, 1 September 2015 (9 minutes ago) The State Department has released more than 7,000 more emails from Hillary Rodham Clinton's time as Secretary of State. They include 125 emails that were censored prior to being released because they contain information now considered classified.
